ing of plasmon-enhanced Raman scattering\nand opens a route to molecular quantum optomechanics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Jul 2014 17:49:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 6 May 2015 08:19:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2015 11:09:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-10"}
